==Finnish==
===Adjective===
'''vittuuntunut'''

# Angry as a cunt; describing a person experiencing [[vitutus]]. Some females may prefer to use the word ''[[kyrpiintynyt]]'' instead, which is derived from the word for [[prick]].

Derived from [[vittu]].

===Adjective: Comparative degrees===
*''vittuuntuneempi'' "more annoyed [than someone, or at a specified time]". Seldom used
*''vittuuntunein'' "most annoyed [in the group in question]". Very seldom used, almost extinct.

===Related terms===
*[[vittuilija]]
*[[vituttaa]]
*[[vitutus]]

